abstract: >-
  A medium that unifies humans and AIs into a single workspace: recursive Agent
  nodes with one primitive (send) and a universal discovery verb (reflect),
  across four runtimes (python, swift, rust host kernels + a ts browser
  frontend). Capabilities emerge from self-description — given only the readmes,
  an AI weaves the wiring itself.
